00:28:30,125 --> 00:28:31,626
[riffling through books]

454
00:28:35,422 --> 00:28:36,297
[unzips]

455
00:28:40,093 --> 00:28:41,553
[clicking pen]

456
00:28:43,430 --> 00:28:44,848
[pen scribbling]

457
00:28:51,312 --> 00:28:53,440
[Eun-jung] <i>Blue can mean that you're sad.</i>

458
00:28:53,982 --> 00:28:55,567
<i>I'm just too pessimistic.</i>

459
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:00,238
Eun-jung.

460
00:29:02,031 --> 00:29:03,992
What do you like most in this world?

461
00:29:05,744 --> 00:29:07,829
[adult Eun-jung] <i>Since</i>
<i>our tutoring sessions began…</i>

462
00:29:07,912 --> 00:29:08,788
Who, me?

463
00:29:10,248 --> 00:29:13,585
<i>…this was the first time</i>
<i>he initiated a conversation.</i>

464
00:29:13,668 --> 00:29:14,627
Well,

465
00:29:15,462 --> 00:29:17,630
the thing I love most in this world…

466
00:29:18,882 --> 00:29:20,300
Uh…

467
00:29:21,134 --> 00:29:23,011
I think it's <i>Wink</i>, yeah.

468
00:29:23,887 --> 00:29:24,888
<i>"Wink"</i>?

469
00:29:25,388 --> 00:29:28,308
It's a <i>manhwa.</i>
It comes out every two weeks.

470
00:29:28,391 --> 00:29:29,476
Ah…

471
00:29:29,559 --> 00:29:31,436
[Eun-jung] I like <i>Wink, </i>H.O.T.,

472
00:29:31,519 --> 00:29:34,063
and I love dogs,
but my mom won't let me have one.

473
00:29:35,148 --> 00:29:36,566
I like corn a bunch too.

474
00:29:37,317 --> 00:29:40,361
Oops, I forgot my mom. I love my mom too.

475
00:29:41,029 --> 00:29:44,407
I like Sang-yeon, Na-mi,
Ju-eun, and a bunch of friends.

476
00:29:44,908 --> 00:29:46,201
And Ms. Yoon too.

477
00:29:46,785 --> 00:29:49,078
Your mom is such a good person.

478
00:29:50,705 --> 00:29:51,956
Also…

479
00:29:58,713 --> 00:30:00,131
our tutoring sessions.

480
00:30:01,633 --> 00:30:03,259
[sweet music playing]

481
00:30:08,807 --> 00:30:09,808
[chuckles softly]

482
00:30:12,018 --> 00:30:13,019
[Sang-hak chuckles]

483
00:30:17,190 --> 00:30:18,274
What?

484
00:30:18,983 --> 00:30:20,318
It's just Eun-jung.

